title: GGinParis

content_html: Mike Cernovich, Milo Yiannopoulos, and I will be at GGinParis on Saturday, July 11 at 8 PM. If you’re in Europe, or if you’re going to be in Europe this summer, and intend to come, please shoot me an email with GGinParis in the subject.
